dct_title_s: Tafel des Heiligen Landes zu dem Newen Testament dienlich
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, settlements, places of historical interest.
Features illustrations of settlements and sea monsters.
